I'm Pastor Jerome Hancock and I want to say hi to everyone. It's good to be with you today. Hey, you see this thing in my hand right here?

00:00:53.408 --> 00:01:03.456
i found this out in my yard. it's amazing. we have this big storm where i live and it just tore up everything and i went out in the yard.

00:01:02.976 --> 00:01:13.024
Hard after the storm and my chain ring fence. You know those metal fences that people have around their houses? I have one of those. It was all torn up and the metal was all mangled. And there, oh.

00:01:12.544 --> 00:01:22.592
On top of it all was this thing and I couldn't believe it I've never seen anything like it in my whole life and I thought man this is amazing

00:01:22.112 --> 00:01:32.160
Amazing that this thing could accidentally come out of a storm. Isn't that amazing? Can you believe it? I've never seen anything like it. It's probably the only one.

00:01:31.680 --> 00:01:33.760
1 in the world.

00:01:33.408 --> 00:01:34.080
Oh.

